Φ(EpistemicJusticeISTF) = σ(distinction|silenced-vs-heard-epistemologies) ∘ ρ(resonance|structural-inaudibility-felt-absence) ∘ μ(structure|cognitive-infrastructure-redesign) ∘ β(branching|narrative-multiplicity-plural-ontologies) ∘ λ(direction|from-access-to-co-authorship) ∘ δγ(cycling|ritualized-reflection-epistemic-audits) + ε | :weaving

// Nemetic String Components:
// σ (Air/Distinction): Distinguishing silenced from heard epistemologies
// ρ (Water/Resonance): Feeling structural inaudibility, the quality of not-being-heard
// μ (Metal/Structure): Redesigning cognitive infrastructure, platform protocols
// β (Wood/Branching): Narrative multiplicity, plural ontologies, epistemic diversity
// λ (Fire/Direction): Transformation from access to co-authorship
// δγ (Earth/Cycling): Ritualized reflection, epistemic audits, iterative learning
// ε (Void/Ether): Emergent property of weaving
// Z-State: :weaving — continuous co-creation of knowledge tapestries
